{
  "text": "In other words, each statistic represents the degree of congruence between the growth simulated by the model and the landuse evolution observed from time series of historical data. In our case study the mean to assess the best set of coefficients during the calibration process is the Optimum SLEUTH Metric method [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
  "correct_citation": {
